---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<BaseHead 
		title={`About Hermetrix | New Zealand Privacy & Security Specialists`} 
		description="New Zealand-focused security company understanding threats unique to Kiwi businesses and individuals. Local expertise in NZ privacy challenges, compliance, and practical security implementation."
		keywords="New Zealand security threats, NZ privacy company, local security experts, Aotearoa digital privacy, NZ cyber security, privacy solutions New Zealand"
	/>
</head>
<body>
	<a href="#main-content" class="skip-to-main">Skip to main content</a>
	<Header />
	<main id="main-content">
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>About Hermetrix</h1>
				<p class="tagline">Understanding New Zealand's unique security landscape</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Security Tailored for Aotearoa</h2>
				<p>Hermetrix is a recently established New Zealand security company built on a simple premise: New Zealand companies and individuals face distinct privacy and security challenges that require local understanding, not generic global solutions.</p>
				<p>We're not trying to compete on the global stage. Instead, we focus on implementing the right products and practices that work for New Zealanders - understanding our local threat landscape, compliance requirements, and the unique position of being a small, geographically isolated nation in an interconnected digital world.</p>
				<p><strong>Most importantly, we're committed to making privacy easy and economical for everyone in New Zealand.</strong> Whether you're a student, small business owner, or large enterprise, effective privacy protection should be accessible and tailored to your actual needs - not oversold or unnecessarily complex.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Understanding New Zealand's Threat Landscape</h2>
				<p class="intro-text">New Zealanders and Kiwi businesses face security challenges that don't map cleanly to overseas models:</p>
				
				<div class="grid grid-2">
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Data Sovereignty Challenges</h3>
						<p>Most global cloud services store Kiwi data overseas, subject to foreign laws like the US CLOUD Act or Australia's Assistance and Access Act. We help you understand what this means for your privacy and when local or encrypted alternatives make sense.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Small Market Disadvantages</h3>
						<p>Major security vendors often deprioritize NZ. Updates arrive late, support is offshore, and pricing doesn't reflect our market. We identify products and practices that actually work within New Zealand's constraints.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Geographic Isolation</h3>
						<p>Being at the bottom of the world means hardware takes longer to arrive, specialist support isn't local, and you can't just "drop by" a vendor's office. We provide realistic security solutions that account for these realities.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card">
						<h3>Regulatory Navigation</h3>
						<p>Understanding how the Privacy Act, NZISM, and sector-specific requirements apply to your situation - without the complexity of global compliance frameworks that don't match our context.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="emphasis-box">
					<h2>Why Local Understanding Matters</h2>
					<p>A Wellington professional has different security needs than a Silicon Valley tech worker. An Auckland small business faces different threats than a San Francisco startup. A Christchurch family's privacy concerns aren't identical to those in London.</p>
					<p>We understand:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>How New Zealand's Privacy Act actually applies in practice, not just theory</li>
						<li>Which international security products have reliable NZ supply chains</li>
						<li>The real costs and timeframes for getting security hardware into the country</li>
						<li>Local threat patterns targeting Kiwi businesses and individuals</li>
						<li>When offshore cloud storage creates genuine risk vs. theoretical concern</li>
						<li>How to balance security needs with New Zealand's practical realities</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Our Approach</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-3">
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Easy Implementation</h3>
						<p>We make privacy simple. No frameworks, no jargon-filled reports. Just working solutions that fit your life or business, implemented in ways that actually make sense.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Economical & Honest</h3>
						<p>Privacy shouldn't break the bank. We recommend solutions based on your actual needs and budget. If a $50 solution works, we won't sell you a $5,000 one. No upselling, no vendor commissions.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-card">
						<h3>Tailored to Your Needs</h3>
						<p>A student's privacy needs differ from a law firm's. We assess your specific situation and recommend appropriate protection - nothing more, nothing less.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>What We Do</h2>
				<div class="focus-areas">
					<div class="grid grid-2">
						<div class="focus-item">
							<h3>Security Assessments for NZ Context</h3>
							<p>We evaluate your security posture through a New Zealand lens - understanding local compliance needs, realistic threat models for Kiwi organizations, and practical implementation within NZ constraints.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="focus-item">
							<h3>Certified Hardware Access</h3>
							<p>We source and supply FIPS-certified encrypted storage, privacy-focused smartphones, and other security hardware that's difficult to obtain in New Zealand - handling the complexity of international procurement and local setup.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="focus-item">
							<h3>Privacy-Focused Mobile Devices</h3>
							<p>GrapheneOS phones configured specifically for New Zealand users - understanding local carrier compatibility, NZ app requirements, and practical daily use in Aotearoa.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="focus-item">
							<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
							<p>We don't hand you documentation and disappear. We implement solutions with you, provide training in plain language, and remain available for ongoing support.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="trust-section">
					<h2>Why Trust Hermetrix?</h2>
					<div class="trust-content">
						<p><strong>We're Transparent:</strong> New Zealand company (NZBN: 9429052746815), locally operated, no offshore parent companies or investors with conflicting interests.</p>
						<p><strong>We're Focused:</strong> We specialize in security products and practices for New Zealand. This isn't a side service - it's all we do.</p>
						<p><strong>We're Economical:</strong> Privacy protection shouldn't be a luxury. We make it accessible and affordable for all New Zealanders by recommending solutions matched to your needs and budget - no upselling, no vendor commissions.</p>
						<p><strong>We're Practical:</strong> We recommend solutions we'd use ourselves. If a $50 solution solves your problem, we won't sell you a $5,000 one. Privacy should be easy to understand and implement.</p>
						<p><strong>We're Local:</strong> Based in Auckland, serving all of New Zealand. We understand our market because we're part of it.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="container text-center">
				<h2>Let's Talk About Your Security</h2>
				<p>Whether you're an individual concerned about privacy or a business navigating New Zealand's security requirements, we're here to help with straightforward advice and practical implementation.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz" class="btn primary">Get in Touch</a>
					<a href="/products" class="btn secondary">View Products</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer />

	<style>
		.hero {
			padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			margin-top: var(--space-md);
			font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		}

		.card {
			background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
		}

		.intro-text {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
			line-height: 1.7;
		}

		.emphasis-box {
			padding: var(--space-2xl);
			background: rgba(153, 51, 204, 0.03);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			border: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
			border-radius: 8px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(153, 51, 204, 0.08);
		}

		.emphasis-box h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			text-align: center;
		}

		.emphasis-box p {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
			margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
		}

		.emphasis-box ul {
			margin-top: var(--space-lg);
		}

		.emphasis-box li {
			font-size: 1.0625rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
		}

		.trust-section {
			padding: var(--space-2xl);
			background: rgba(51, 153, 153, 0.03);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			border: 2px solid var(--accent-secondary);
			border-radius: 8px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(51, 153, 153, 0.08);
		}

		.trust-section h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
			color: var(--accent-secondary);
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
		}

		.trust-content p {
			font-size: 1.0625rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
			margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
		}

		.trust-content p:last-child {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}

		.trust-content strong {
			color: var(--accent-secondary);
			font-weight: 700;
		}

		.feature-card {
			padding: var(--space-xl);
			border: 2px solid var(--white);
			border-radius: 6px;
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
			backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
			box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			position: relative;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		.feature-card::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			left: 50%;
			width: 0;
			height: 0;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--magenta) 0%, transparent 70%);
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
			transition: all 0.5s ease;
			z-index: 0;
		}

		.feature-card:hover {
			border-color: var(--accent-primary);
			transform: translate(-1px, -1px);
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(153, 51, 204, 0.15);
		}

		.feature-card:hover::before {
			width: 200%;
			height: 200%;
			opacity: 0.02;
		}

		.feature-card h3 {
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
			font-weight: 900;
			position: relative;
			z-index: 1;
		}

		.feature-card p {
			margin: 0;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
			position: relative;
			z-index: 1;
		}

		.focus-areas {
			padding: var(--space-2xl);
			background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
			backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			border-radius: 8px;
			border: 2px solid var(--white);
			box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
		}

		.focus-areas h2 {
			margin-top: 0;
			text-align: center;
			font-weight: 900;
			color: var(--accent-secondary);
		}

		.focus-item {
			padding: var(--space-lg);
		}

		.focus-item h3 {
			color: var(--accent-primary);
			margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
			font-weight: 900;
		}

		.focus-item p {
			margin: 0;
			color: var(--text-secondary);
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			display: flex;
			gap: var(--space-lg);
			justify-content: center;
			margin-top: var(--space-xl);
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.hero {
				padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
			}

			.tagline {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.grid-2, .grid-3 {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.card {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.feature-card {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.feature-card:hover {
				transform: translate(-1px, -1px);
				box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.3);
			}

			.focus-areas {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.focus-item {
				padding: var(--space-md);
			}

			.cta-buttons {
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: stretch;
			}

			.emphasis-box {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.emphasis-box p,
			.emphasis-box li {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.trust-section {
				padding: var(--space-lg);
			}

			.trust-content p {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			.hero {
				padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
			}

			.card {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.feature-card {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.focus-areas {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.focus-item {
				padding: var(--space-sm);
			}

			.emphasis-box {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.emphasis-box p,
			.emphasis-box li {
				font-size: 0.9375rem;
			}

			.trust-section {
				padding: var(--space-md);
				border-width: 2px;
			}

			.trust-content p {
				font-size: 0.9375rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</body>
</html>

